Plateau chairman of the All Progressives Congress(APC) Hon Letep Dabang has recovered from COVID-19. He tested negative after being in isolation since December 23, 2020. A visibly elated Dabang thanked God for his recovery, attributing it to the prayers of Plateau residents. Recalling his ordeal while in isolation, the APC chairman said COVID-19 is real and Nigerians must follow laid down protocols on safety by relevant agencies. He prayed God to continually guide Plateau residents and Nigerians in battling the scourge.